<item>
            <title>[LU-13337] How to detach all files from PCC device</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13337</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a user writes a large number of files on the PCC device, currently there is no way to get a listing of those cached files. The user must keep track of the files there could be cases where a user may lost track of some files.&lt;br/&gt;
Are there plans to add functionality for list of files on the PCC? &lt;br/&gt;
Currently, is there a backend way to find all those files? Or to detach all files?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;</description>
